data.description: Craftsman home on 20 acres w spacious 3 BD 1.5 BA almost 2400 sq feet is complete w alternative power, kubota backup diesel generator, 2 wells, spring fed pond, fenced pastures with 50X60 barn, chicken coop and room for horses. This property has the remote feel while being only approx 12 miles from town, on county road w amazing views of the Purcell Mountain range! Come see this beautiful place before its gone!
